consensus text: When we see one body presenting
a moving a variable sensation, striking
against another body so as to produce
motion on it we call it cause
& effect we call the motion connected
ie when we have uniformly beheld
two ideas associated together we call
to the order of association well
they are no longer necessarily connected
scepticism with regard to theory is
